1178
01:27:06,776 --> 01:27:08,642
Hey, Takeshi!

1179
01:27:11,347 --> 01:27:12,576
Takeshi!

1180
01:27:15,485 --> 01:27:18,512
Smile, go ahead and laugh!

1181
01:27:19,355 --> 01:27:19,845
