1187
01:28:52,949 --> 01:28:54,008
Yes.

1188
01:28:54,283 --> 01:28:57,879
Miracles are miracles. Do you have one?

1189
01:28:58,855 --> 01:29:02,383
My grandpa came back to life.

1190
01:29:02,558 --> 01:29:03,890
Really.

1191
01:29:04,894 --> 01:29:07,090
