and at his funeral I kept thinking...

1193
01:29:13,970 --> 01:29:16,667
...something just smells terrible.

1194
01:29:16,873 --> 01:29:20,105
And families sit close to the coffin.

1195
01:29:20,209 --> 01:29:21,609
Yeah they do.

1196
01:29:23,279 --> 01:29:24,975
You figure it out?

1197
01:29:26,682 --> 01:29:30,119
I think everyone smelt it.

1198
01:29:30,219 --> 01:29:35,624
Next to my father whose arms
were around me because I won't sit still...

1199
01:29:35,725 --> 01:29:37,421
...holding me down.

1200
01:29:37,960 --> 01:29:39,428
Sounds unlike you.

1201
01:29:39,862 --> 01:29:44,061
