his consciousness...

1219
01:30:50,232 --> 01:30:53,259
...passed away after 3 years in bed.

1220
01:30:54,770 --> 01:30:57,535
My mom was also a teacher but...

1221
01:30:58,140 --> 01:31:01,577
...had to quit to take care of him.

1222
01:31:02,645 --> 01:31:07,310
