but my family could have stayed happy...

1226
01:31:26,736 --> 01:31:29,831
Not your fault. It really smelled, right?

1227
01:31:31,040 --> 01:31:31,973
Yeah.

1228
01:31:32,074 --> 01:31:33,872
See, not your fault.

1229
01:31:36,278 --> 01:31:39,680
